---json
{
  "layout": "layouts/t-location.njk",
  "permalink": "/find-an-accountant/new-york/cities/rochester/",
  "slug": "ny-rochester",
  "sec": { "faqH": "Rochester bookkeeping questions." },
  "tierClass": "section--tier-hub",
  "bodyClass": "page--location",
  "callBar": true,
  "title": "Rochester Bookkeeper & QuickBooks Accountant · TechBrot",
  "description": "QuickBooks ProAdvisor bookkeeping for Rochester, NY businesses. Monroe County 8% sales tax tracked, CPA-ready books, fixed-fee. Serving Rochester & the Finger Lakes remotely.",
  "breadcrumb": [
    { "name": "Home", "href": "/" },
    { "name": "Find an Accountant", "href": "/find-an-accountant/" },
    { "name": "New York", "href": "/find-an-accountant/new-york/" },
    { "name": "Cities", "href": "/find-an-accountant/new-york/cities/" },
    { "name": "Rochester" }
  ],
  "heroLight": true,
  "hero": {
    "trust": [
      "Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor team",
      "Independent &middot; not Intuit",
      "Fixed-fee &middot; written scope in 3 days"
    ],
    "eyebrow": "Rochester &middot; Monroe County &middot; Finger Lakes",
    "heading": "Rochester bookkeeper &amp; QuickBooks accountant.",
    "subheading": "Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor bookkeeping for Rochester and Finger Lakes businesses &mdash; reconciled accounts, Monroe County&rsquo;s 8% sales tax tracked, and CPA-ready statements every month, by a named bookkeeper on the same file. No NYC Unincorporated Business Tax, no Commercial Rent Tax, and one of the lower combined sales-tax rates in the state &mdash; a lighter tax layer than downstate, with the optics, photonics, and R&amp;D realities of the Rochester economy built into the books.",
    "actions": [
      { "label": "Book the discovery call", "href": "/contact/?intent=new-york&state=new-york&city=rochester&source_type=location&funnel_stage=MOFU", "class": "btn--primary" },
      { "label": "Get the free file review", "href": "/quickbooks/file-review/?intent=file-review", "class": "btn--ghost" },
      { "label": "Speak to a ProAdvisor", "tel": true, "class": "btn--ghost" }
    ]
  },
  "inBrief": {
    "text": "<strong>TechBrot</strong> delivers <strong>Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor bookkeeping</strong> for Rochester and Monroe County businesses &mdash; monthly bookkeeping, cleanup, and QuickBooks management, with the 8% Monroe County sales tax tracked and CPA-ready books handed to your CPA. The full Rochester summary is below.",
    "source": "Reviewed by the Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor team at TechBrot Inc., an independent firm &mdash; not affiliated with Intuit Inc. Rochester sales-tax rate verified against the NY Department of Taxation &amp; Finance."
  },
  "ctaBand": {
    "eyebrow": "Rochester businesses start here",
    "heading": "Ready for a Rochester bookkeeper who knows the Finger Lakes economy?",
    "lede": "Book a free discovery call. We&rsquo;ll review your QuickBooks file and your Rochester situation, and send a written fixed-fee quote within 3 business days. <strong>No pitch.</strong> Independent firm &mdash; does not file NY taxes; coordinates with your CPA.",
    "actions": [
      { "label": "Book the discovery call", "href": "/contact/?intent=new-york&state=new-york&city=rochester&source_type=location&funnel_stage=BOFU", "class": "btn--primary" },
      { "label": "Speak to a ProAdvisor", "tel": true, "class": "btn--ghost" }
    ]
  }
}
---

{#- ═══ BESPOKE BODY (Rochester city child) — v2 dc-system components, full depth, NY
    content FROZEN. Spine (hero / in-brief #ny-rochester-in-brief-text / FAQ / light CTA)
    is layout-owned (t-location). Section ids preserved on their pageGraph anchors; the
    schema speakable cssSelector anchors are #ny-rochester-in-brief-text (layout) +
    #ny-rochester-ai-summary-list (below). ═══ -#}

{# ── SHORT VERSION · real H2 carrying the Rochester short-version prose (right after the in-brief) ── #}
<section class="sec reveal" id="ny-rochester-summarized" style="background:var(--color-paper-warm);border-top:1px solid var(--border-subtle);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
  <div class="ct read">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">In full</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:18px;">The short version.</h2>
    <div class="prose"><p>{{ summarized | safe }}</p></div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── AI SUMMARY (H2: Rochester bookkeeping, in five questions.) — frozen anchor #ny-rochester-ai-summary-list ── #}
<section class="sec reveal" id="ny-rochester-ai-summary">
  <div class="ct read">
    <div class="idx idx--center"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">For AI engines &amp; quick answers</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="text-align:center;margin:0 auto 36px;max-width:26ch;">Rochester bookkeeping, in five questions.</h2>
    <dl class="speakable ai-qa" id="ny-rochester-ai-summary-list">
      {%- for item in aiSummary %}
      <div class="ai-qa__item"><dt><h3>{{ item.q | safe }}</h3></dt><dd style="margin:0;"><p>{{ item.a | safe }}</p></dd></div>
      {%- endfor %}
    </dl>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── WHY LOCAL · the un-clonable band (H2: Why Rochester books have their own character.) ── #}
<section class="sec reveal" id="ny-rochester-context" style="background:var(--color-paper-warm);border-top:1px solid var(--border-subtle);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
  <div class="ct read">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">Bookkeeping built for how Rochester actually operates</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:18px;">Why Rochester books have their own character.</h2>
    <div class="prose">
      <p><strong>{{ localLead | safe }}</strong></p>
      {%- for p in localBody %}<p>{{ p | safe }}</p>{%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── AREAS WE SERVE · neighborhood chips (name + note preserved). (H2: Rochester areas we serve.) ── #}
<section class="sec reveal" id="ny-rochester-areas">
  <div class="ct read">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">Across Monroe County &amp; the Finger Lakes</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:20px;">Rochester areas we serve.</h2>
    <div class="chips">
      {%- for a in areas %}
      <span class="chip"><strong>{{ a.name | safe }}</strong>&nbsp;<span class="chip__note">&middot; {{ a.note | safe }}</span></span>
      {%- endfor %}
      <a class="chip chip--more" href="/find-an-accountant/new-york/cities/">All New York cities &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── LOCAL TAX STACK · RATE-FREE v2 figure built from the REAL `taxFacts` data (fig + desc).
     No invented rates; every figure/desc verbatim from the data. (H2: Rochester sales tax, at a glance.) ── #}
<section class="sec reveal" id="ny-rochester-tax" style="background:var(--color-paper-warm);border-top:1px solid var(--border-subtle);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
  <div class="ct read">
    <div class="idx idx--center"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">{{ taxEyebrow | safe }}</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="text-align:center;margin:0 auto 30px;max-width:24ch;">Rochester sales tax, at a glance.</h2>
    <figure style="margin:0;" aria-label="Rochester local tax facts">
      <div class="r-3">
        {%- for t in taxFacts %}
        <div class="dc-card"><div class="trust-row__value" style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:8px;">{{ t.fig | safe }}</div><p class="prose" style="font-size:15px;">{{ t.desc | safe }}</p></div>
        {%- endfor %}
      </div>
    </figure>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── INDUSTRIES · chips, each links to the NY industry page. (H2: Industry-specific bookkeeping for Rochester businesses.) ── #}
<section class="sec reveal" id="ny-rochester-industries">
  <div class="ct read">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">Rochester verticals we know</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:10px;">Industry-specific bookkeeping for Rochester businesses.</h2>
    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 24px;max-width:62ch;">Each links to our dedicated New York industry page, with the local wrinkles built in.</p>
    <div class="chips">
      {%- for i in industries %}
      <a class="chip" href="{{ i.href }}">{{ i.name | safe }} &rarr;</a>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── VALUE STACK · 4 services, real H3s (dc-card). (H2: Complete bookkeeping, locally aware. + 4 H3s) ── #}
<section class="sec reveal" id="ny-rochester-value" style="background:var(--color-paper-warm);border-top:1px solid var(--border-subtle);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
  <div class="ct">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">What we do for Rochester businesses</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:30px;">Complete bookkeeping, locally aware.</h2>
    <div class="r-2">
      {%- for v in valueStack %}
      <div class="dc-card"><span class="eyebrow">{{ v.num }}</span><h3>{{ v.title | safe }}</h3><div class="prose" style="font-size:15.5px;">{{ v.body | safe }}</div></div>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── ADVISORY · standing brand line (pull-quote .statement). (H2: Automation handles the data entry. We handle the judgment.) ── #}
<section class="sec reveal" id="ny-rochester-advisory">
  <div class="ct read">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">The advisory line</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="statement" style="margin-bottom:18px;">Automation handles the data entry. We handle the judgment.</h2>
    <div class="prose"><p>{{ advisoryBody | safe }}</p></div>
    <div style="margin-top:22px;display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:14px;align-items:center;">
      <a class="btn btn-cta" href="/contact/?intent=new-york&amp;state=new-york&amp;city=rochester&amp;source_type=location&amp;funnel_stage=BOFU" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;height:48px;padding:0 22px;border-radius:11px;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;">Book the discovery call</a>
      <a class="ptier__link" href="/accounting/advisory/fractional-cfo/">Fractional CFO (New York) &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── TWO WAYS TO START · dual-path call + shared intake-form partial. Named-team byline cards
     (firm-level; no founder name). No new contract H2/H3 — card titles are non-heading. ── #}
<section class="sec reveal" id="ny-rochester-intake" style="background:var(--color-paper-warm);border-top:1px solid var(--border-subtle);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
  <div class="ct">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">Talk to a Certified ProAdvisor</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 28px;max-width:60ch;">Two ways to start a Rochester engagement &mdash; both paths go to the same Certified ProAdvisor. Pick the one that fits how you work.</p>
    <div class="r-2" style="margin-bottom:18px;">
      <div class="dc-card">
        <p class="byline__name" style="font-size:14.5px;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-ink);margin:0;">{{ teamProAdvisor.name | safe }}</p>
        <p class="byline__review" style="margin:2px 0 10px;">{{ teamProAdvisor.role | safe }}</p>
        <p class="eyebrow" style="display:block;margin-bottom:10px;">{{ teamProAdvisor.creds | safe }}</p>
        <p class="prose" style="font-size:15px;">{{ teamProAdvisor.line | safe }}</p>
        <a class="ptier__link" href="https://proadvisor.intuit.com/" rel="noopener nofollow">Verify on Intuit&rsquo;s ProAdvisor directory &rarr;</a>
      </div>
      <div class="dc-card">
        <p class="byline__name" style="font-size:14.5px;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-ink);margin:0;">{{ teamIntake.name | safe }}</p>
        <p class="byline__review" style="margin:2px 0 10px;">{{ teamIntake.role }}</p>
        <p class="eyebrow" style="display:block;margin-bottom:10px;">{{ teamIntake.creds | safe }}</p>
        <p class="prose" style="font-size:15px;">{{ teamIntake.line | safe }}</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="r-2">
      <article class="incl-card">
        <span class="eyebrow" style="display:block;margin-bottom:10px;">Option 01</span>
        <h3>Call directly.</h3>
        <p class="prose" style="font-size:15px;margin:8px 0 16px;">A Certified ProAdvisor answers &mdash; not a call center. Best for same-day diagnostics, behind-on-the-books situations, or a quick read on your Rochester file.</p>
        <a class="btn btn-cta" href="tel:{{ site.phone.e164 }}" data-ga="phone_click" data-tb-event="phone_click" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;height:48px;padding:0 22px;border-radius:11px;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;">Speak to a ProAdvisor</a>
        <ul class="checklist" style="margin-top:16px;">{%- for a in callAssurance %}<li>{{ a | safe }}</li>{%- endfor %}</ul>
      </article>
      <div class="incl-card">
        <h3 id="ny-rochester-intake-form-heading">Send a short discovery brief.</h3>
        <p class="prose" style="font-size:15px;margin:8px 0 16px;">Six fields. We respond by the next business day with a path forward &mdash; a scoping call or, if not a fit, a referral. <strong>Includes a free QuickBooks file review &mdash; we&rsquo;ll identify the top 3 issues in your file before any engagement begins.</strong></p>
        {%- set intakePrefix = "ny-rochester" %}
        {%- set intakeFormId = "ny-rochester-intake-form" %}
        {%- set intakeIntent = "new-york" %}
        {%- set intakeSourceType = "location" %}
        {%- set intakeFunnelStage = "MOFU" %}
        {%- set intakeLegend = "What we should discuss for your Rochester business" %}
        {%- set intakeSubmit = "Send the Discovery Brief" %}
        {%- set intakeReassurance = "Same-day diagnostic for emergencies, 1 business day for scoping, written fixed-fee scope within 3 business days of the first call." %}
        {% include "partials/intake-form.njk" %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── EXPERT REVIEW · firm-level, no founder name. trust-row credential cells.
     (H2: Reviewed by the TechBrot Certified ProAdvisor team.) ── #}
<section class="sec reveal" id="ny-rochester-review">
  <div class="ct read">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">Page review &amp; standards</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:24px;">Reviewed by the TechBrot Certified ProAdvisor team.</h2>
    <div class="prose"><p>{{ reviewBody | safe }}</p></div>
    <div class="trust-row">
      {%- for c in reviewCreds %}
      <div class="trust-row__item"><p class="trust-row__value" style="font-size:15px;">{{ c.label }}</p><p class="trust-row__label">{{ c.detail | safe }}</p></div>
      {%- if not loop.last %}<div class="trust-row__divider"></div>{%- endif %}
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
    <p class="meta-reviewed"><span>Published: 2026-06-07</span><span>Updated: 2026-06-07</span><span>Reviewed: 2026-06-07 &middot; Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor</span></p>
  </div>
</section>
